      <title>尼日利亚的管道危机将在总统的权力抢夺下恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-03-24/nigeria-s-oil-pipeline-crisis-will-worsen-with-tinubu-s-emergency-declaration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宣布石油丰富的河流州的紧急状态是误导的。该地区的问题是政治的，军队的镇压无济于事。]]></description>
